								<h2>Every penny counts</h2>
								<p>There are a number of ways to support those affected by breast cancer. Whether helping the community as a whole or donating in honor of or in memory of a loved one, each donation helps sustain our mission to educate the community and fight to end breast cancer.  </p>


								<h2>Honorary Donation</h2>
								<p>Honor a loved one with your best research gift. Your contributions power the efforts of nearly 275 researchers worldwide who are answering breast cancer’s most difficult questions. Simply check the “Dedicate my donation in honor of someone” box on our online donation form. At your request, we can send the honoree an email of recognition. </p>

								<h2>Memorial Donation</h2>
								<p>Commemorate a loved one by making a donation in her or his name. When you give to BCRF, you’re powering the world’s best breast cancer research—the one and only way we can hope to gain ground against this devastating disease. Too many loved ones are waiting, still, for the next important breakthrough. We’re standing ready to bring it about—but we need your help.</p>

